INSERT INTO `cost_payments` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `category`) VALUES
(1, 'Check remaining credit and bonuses available to customers Prepaid', 'The remaining credit available, the offers and the status of active bonus on your rechargeable line, are available through the following ways:\r\n<br><br>\r\nRight from your Smartphone, signing into the MyTIM Mobile, currently available for free download in versions for iPhone and smartphones with Android operating system.\r\n<br><br>\r\nTim.it directly online on the website under MyTIM Mobile reserved for our clients that allows you to check the remaining credit, the amount of minutes, SMS, GB still available, in euro bonus that may be present and make changes on your telephone line;\r\nBy calling the freephone number 40916, for the remaining credit. Also typing the key 1 can know the active offers, the amount of minutes, SMS, GB still available and in the euro bonus, if any;\r\nThrough the free service 119sms; by sending an SMS to 119 "free text" (eg "What is my remaining credit") the service will respond with a text message with the requested information;\r\nThrough the activation of the free service "TIM Warn You - info sms" that lets you know the cost of the last call made national and the remaining balance updated in real time by receiving a text message directly on your mobile, or with the service "TIM Warn you - offers" you can be informed by a free text message when consumption of your active offers reaches the percentage of your choice;\r\n<br><br>\r\nIf your on-line there are offers and bonuses in Euros, the consumer priorities generally follows the following criteria:\r\n1. Minutes, SMS, GB included active in the offer;<br><\r\n2. Bonus in EUR with maturity;<br>\r\n2. Bonus in Euros without expiration;<br>\r\n3. Remaining credits.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn the presence of two or more bonus priority is the one with the most immediate expiration.\r\n<br><br>\r\nWe remind you that in the euro bonus can not be used for international calls, for calls to non-geographic numbers (in Italy and abroad) and for roaming traffic (with the exception of traffic data roaming).\r\n<br><br>\r\nFor more details on the conditions of use of the euro in bonus present on your line, see the relevant page in the section of the site offers tim.it.\r\n<br><br>\r\nWe remind you that in order to take advantage of the offers and any euro in bonuses on the line, the remaining credit of your SIM must be greater than zero.', 'cost'),
(2, 'Call detail for rechargeable customers', 'The "traffic documentation" service offers you a chance to get the details of every phone call, data connection or other event conducted by your line (*). For each event is provided indicating the date / time of execution, the cost, the type, the number called and whether it is voice or SMS traffic (with the last three digits asterisked - L. 171/98 "privacy protection telecommunications ").\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe documentation of the traffic is always available in MyTIM Mobile and available up to two months prior to the date of execution of traffic if you use a rechargeable line, easily available in different formats and archived (as pdf).\r\n<br><br>\r\nYou can still request to send a hard copy printout of the previous traffic (equivalent to the already available in pdf MyTIM Mobile), or sending a printout of plain previous traffic (in this case must be specified), as long as falls within periods indicated above. In this case you will need to complete and submit the form "Request Documentation Traffic" which can be downloaded in pdf format from the section modules, selecting the reference rechargeable subsection.\r\n<br><br>\r\n(*) Some types of traffic, for which there is not a cost, can not be documented.', 'cost'),
(4, 'The domiciliation of the current account for rechargeable customers', 'If you need to change the credit card used for payment of your bids domiciled (eg. If you have an active installment for the purchase of a mobile phone) you can do it directly online for the following credit cards: American Express, Cartasi, KeyClient, Bankamericard, Aura-Findomestic Charter, Unicredit, Intesa-Setefi Bank.\r\nFor credit cards of Visa and Mastercard circuits not listed above stated you should instead visit an TIM Store is where you want to change the credit card used for payment of domiciled offers (eg. If you changed the bank or operator of credit card) and in the case that your credit card has been renewed following the expiry of the validity period.\r\n<br><br>\r\nWe remind you that the exchange of credit card operation is always free and that has to be performed in the period in which the offer is active.', 'cost'),
(3, 'Learn how to check the consumption of the line with your subscription', 'You can consult the consumption of your subscription\r\n<br><br> \r\nDirectly online<br>\r\nBy registering to MyTIM Mobile you can check, correct at the date shown on the site:<br>\r\n1. Traffic ITEM, which is composed of:\r\n"National Traffic Voice" is the amount that includes calls made from Italy to national numbers, and to special numbers.<br>\r\n"International Voice Traffic" is the amount that includes calls made from Italy to foreign numbers.<br>\r\n"Traffic Voice PayForMe": it is the total amount of voice traffic carried using the call charge of the service "4088 PayForMe".<br>\r\n"Roaming traffic (Voice)": is the amount of calls made and received abroad.\r\n2. SMS / MMS traffic, which includes:\r\n"SMS Traffic" is the amount that includes the text messages sent to mobile numbers and landline.<br>\r\n"Traffic MMS" is the amount that includes multimedia messaging (MMS) sent to mobile numbers and landline.<br>\r\n3. Other data traffic / Interactive Services, which includes:<br>\r\n"Navigation wap" is the amount that includes the traffic made for the transmission of data / internet connection using the WAP mode (access point to the data network to connect: wap.tim.it).<br>\r\n"Other" data traffic is the amount that includes the traffic made for the transmission of data / internet connection using all other access to the data network points.<br>\r\n"Access" is the total amount of traffic by Wifi access.<br>\r\n"Interactive services" is the amount that includes the charges for receiving / sending sms / mms by numbers Short special content (eg logos, ring tone, background), text messages used by the service "4088 PayForMe sms", and all additional services not included in the previous counters.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCalling from your mobile phone the freephone number 40915:\r\nIt is important to know that the online traffic refers to consumption not included in the cost of any offers and active promotions on your line. The amounts refer to the period from the first day of the two-month period of reference to the date communicated by telephone.<br>\r\nIf you have activated one or more promotions, the key 2 you can check the remaining of the corresponding bonuses and the friends numbers. This refers to the period between the first day of the current month and the date notified by the voice of the lead voice.', 'cost'),
(5, 'Protection and data traffic block', 'TIM allows you to protect your monthly spending to surf the Internet with your mobile phone , tablet or stick giving you also the possibility to block the data traffic .\r\nIn case you have not activated one of our data and perform web browsing , the protection threshold , which is automatically activated on all lines , will monitor your monthly expenditure and in case of reaching the amount of $60 ( VAT included) the line will be locked to the data traffic to protect you , while the voice service and sMS continue to operate .', 'cost'),
(6, 'My TIM Fixed (cost control)', 'Registrandoti a MyTIM Fisso o scaricando la Applicazione per smartphone e tablet avrai a disposizione tutte le informazioni relative alla tua linea di casa.\r\n<br><br>\r\nPotrai visualizzare i servizi e le offerte attive sulla tua linea telefonica, pagare le tue fatture e avere informazioni relative al traffico.\r\n<br><br>\r\nWhy should I register to MyTIM Fixed or download the App MyTIM Fixed?<br>\r\nFirst of all because it is quick and easy, then, because you have the ability to self-manage your own line!\r\n<br>\r\nFill in the registration form to access our services.\r\n<br>\r\nRegistration is complete and certified if you use a fixed-line connection TIM associated with the tax code to be recorded:\r\n<br><br>\r\nIf you are already a TIM customer can access the Internet using the username and password of TIM Alice Mail or Mail .\r\nIf you sign out of the house or a fixed non TIM online , you will need to call (from the front line) the free number 40 123 option 2.\r\nThe access credentials to the app MyTIM Fixed for smartphones and tablets are the ones with which you signed up MyTIM Fixed.', 'cost'),
(7, 'My online account', 'What''s "My Account Online"?\r\n<br>\r\nIt ''a free service that allows you to display the line of your bill sets directly online, even before it is delivered to the home via mail.\r\nUsing the service "My Account" you can also choose not to receive your invoice on paper, thus saving the costs, if they have requested the domiciliation of bank account / postal payments.\r\n<br><br>\r\nHow to join "My Account Online"\r\n<br>\r\nJoining is very simple. Just sign here and being recorded will be asked to enter your social security number and your email address (which will become your username). If desired, once registered and domiciled paying bills, you can select the option of sending paper elimination of the invoice.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe advantages of "My Account Online"\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe benefits of the service are many:\r\n<br>\r\nyou can check online at any time the bills of the last 12 months with the relative state of charge and with the ability to display them in .pdf format, save them on your PC, they are sent to your e-mail box, to have clarification on the meaning of each item on the invoice;<br>\r\nyou can send to Customer Service fixed-line 187 (eg. reporting of incorrect billing traffic, enabling request or termination of a service, etc.);<br>\r\nyou have more time at your disposal to check the invoice as well as having the certainty of receiving it always and not losing it;<br>\r\nall you have full documentation of your phone calls that you can analyze for selecting the type of call, offer, date, number called, time, length and cost, and you can analyze the trend in consumption over the last 12 months in tabular and graphical form. You can also download the graphs in Excel format;\r\nyou can view the unencrypted traffic on the last four invoices;<br>\r\neach month you''ll notify you via e-mail and text messages, if you provide us with your mobile number, on the availability of the latest bill issued within the MyTIM Fixed section.', 'cost'),
(8, 'My TIM mobile (cost control)', 'In MyTIM Mobile you have to provide all the information you need on your Mobile line.\r\n<br><br>\r\nYou can keep abreast of the offering that TIM has designed for you , see your telephone traffic , check the remaining credit and perform refills , view and pay your bill online.', 'cost');
INSERT INTO `hw_config` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `category`) VALUES
(1, 'Specialized technical assistance with SOSsmartphones', 'SOSsmartphone is the TIM service to all customers, or Rechargeable Subscription, you have to receive specialized, personalized technical assistance for the management of your smartphone or tablet.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThanks to SOSsmartphone service you can talk to an expert who will give you all the advice and "premium" service that you require and that above will be able to remotely connect and operate directly on your device.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe services that will be given for SOSsmartphone are:\r\n<br>\r\nfor data transfer support in case of change phone: example transfer phonebook, photos, text messages;\r\nconsultancy in the use of advanced features of the smartphone;\r\nspecialized assistance on advanced configurations of the smartphone and integration into your home network;\r\nmanage and synchronize your media;\r\nsupport to ensure maximum security;\r\nconservation and protection of your data;\r\ntransfer of content;\r\nupdate of your smartphone;\r\nperforming check-ups.\r\n<br><br>\r\nTo request SOSsmartphone service you can:\r\n<br>\r\nplease call 0458214811 (toll call according to your rate / supply plan);\r\ndownload the App SOS Smartphone APP Store (for iOS) and Google Play (for Android) and request the assistance.\r\nThe SOSsmartphone service provides a cost to intervention from 3 $ (VAT included). The amount will be charged on the invoice if you are a customer with Subscription and will be deducted from the remaining balance if you are a customer Rechargeable.<br>\r\nMay 12 also the SOSsmartphone service is also available by subscription at 2 $ / month. This will give you the assistance you need always available and complete for a year.\r\n<br><br>\r\nWe remind you that in TIM.it Site Support is at your disposal all guides for smartphones configurations, tablets and sticks that allow you, in complete autonomy, to configure your mobile phone to all TIM services. Click here to access and select the make and model of your interest.', 'hw'),
(2, 'Service maps on your mobile phone', 'The map service is used on many of the latest generation phones. In some cases the software is already installed by the manufacturer, while in others you can download the application from the Internet and install it at a later time purchase.\r\n<br>\r\nThe presence of this feature varies depending on the model and the software version of the phone.\r\nThe program maps can be used by all mobile phones equipped with GPS functionality.\r\n<br><br>\r\nFor proper use, it is important to know that the mobile maps function uses a special technology called A-GPS, which means the Internet connection during the use of the service. If you are a customer or rechargeable subscription, see the section devoted to Internet offers and choose the one most suited to your needs. In the absence of un''offerte specification for the data traffic will be applied to the basic rate.', 'hw'),
(3, 'Application store TIM', 'By TIM to have on your mobile applications you want is easier than ever.\r\nWith TIM Application Store I can turn your phone into a handy tool to meet any need: play, be up to date with the latest news and views, communicate with your friends, look for anything that interests you, access to many applications that multiply the functionality of your mobile.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAccess the TIM Application Store from the configured phone with TIM APN (http://timstore.tim.it) or PC (http://www.timstore.it) by registering your phone number, you can personalize your phone by downloading a extensive catalog of applications guaranteed by TIM and compatible with major brands / phone models and operating systems (Android, Symbian, Windows Phone, Blackberry and Java).\r\n<br><br>\r\nBesides downloading the TIM appstore app, a free download directly from the phone (http://timstore.tim.it) or PC (http://www.timstore.it), you will have access to TIM Application Store. TIM appstore allows you to organize the applications you download, receive notifications on your phone''s display and exchange tips on the App of the moment with your friends.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBy accessing the store by phone displays only the content available for the model of phone you use, also if your terminal is not yet supported by the service will open a dedicated information page.\r\nIf you access the site from a PC, once authenticated, TIM Application Store will select for you the applications available for your phone based on the last phone you used on the TIM network; if you want to change the model, select it manually from the menu.\r\n<br><br>\r\nCurrently the service is only available to TIM customers (Private and Company).\r\nDownloaded applications''ll charge your mobile bills online (subscription customers) or remaining credit (rechargeable customers); VAT costs included to download individual applications are indicated next to each published application on the Store.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe WAP browsing costs depend on your profile and any Promotions / active offers. In the absence of a specific offer for the data traffic will be charged at the basic rate.\r\n<br><br>\r\nTIM Application Store is not a subscription service.', 'hw'),
(4, 'Mail setup on iPhone', 'To add your Alice mail account on iPhone, tap the Settings icon from the menu:\r\nIn the Settings:\r\nchoose the voice mail, contacts, calendars\r\nthen Add Account ...\r\nfrom the list of providers visit Others:\r\ntouch Add account Mail\r\nfill in the fields with your details of the Alice mailbox:\r\nName: Enter a name of your choice;\r\nAddress: your full address of the domain @ alice.it;\r\nPassword: enter your email password;\r\nDescription: Enter a name to specify this account (Alice, Home, Office, ...).\r\nFinally, tap the Next button:\r\n<br>\r\nThe iPhone in the next steps automatically checks the account''s existence and proper functioning of the incoming mail server and outgoing:\r\n<br>\r\nIf you see the following warning at the end of the audit; It touches the button to complete the configuration:\r\nTo access the mailbox tap the Mail icon from the main menu and select your account.\r\n<br>\r\nN.B. iPhone configures your alice box automatically according to the protocol IMAPche keeps synchronized your mail with the mail server; in this way also delete your messages from the server occurs only when you make cancellation iPhone. We''ll want to keep this setting.\r\n<br>\r\nIf you need to configure the email on POP3 protocol click below on ''Configure POP3''\r\n<br>\r\nIf you still find it difficult in the configuration, we inform you that our service is available for a fee PC SOS Service: technical agree a personalized intervention personnel to optimally configure your iPhone.', 'hw'),
(5, 'Mail setup on iPad', 'To add your Alice mail account on iPad, tap the Settings icon from the menu:\r\n\r\nhttp://assistenzatecnica.telecomitalia.it/at/ShowBinary?nodePath=/AT_REPOSITORY/Serbatoio/common/images/sg/help/upload/ipa/ipad_imp\r\n\r\nIn the Settings:\r\n\r\nchoose E-mail entry, Contacts, Calendars\r\nthen Add account ... on the right\r\nfrom the list of providers visit Others:\r\n<br><br>\r\ntouch Add account Mail\r\nfill in the fields with your details of the Alice mailbox:<br>\r\nName: Enter a name of your choice;\r\nAddress: your full address of the domain @ alice.it;<br>\r\nPassword: enter your email password;\r\nDescription: Enter a name to specify this account (Alice, Home, Office, ...).\r\nFinally, tap the Save button:\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe iPad in the next steps automatically checks the account''s existence and proper functioning of the incoming mail server and outgoing ( ''I am looking for account'' and ''I check'').\r\n<br>\r\nAfter verification, you may see the following warning in this case touches the Yes button to complete the configuration:\r\n<br><br>\r\nTo access the mailbox tap the Mail icon from the main menu and select your account.\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nIf you''re having trouble sending mail, please select below the voice ''Mailer SMTP outbound''.\r\n<br>\r\nN.B. iPad automatically configures to receive messages from your IMAP Alice box that allows you to keep synchronized the status of your mail with the mail server; in this way also delete your messages from the server occurs only when you make cancellation iPad. We''ll want to keep this setting on your tablet.\r\n<br>\r\nIf you need to configure the reception of messages via the POP3 protocol follow the instructions below under the heading ''POP3 Management''.\r\n<br>\r\nIf you still find it difficult in the configuration, we inform you that our service is available for a fee PC SOS Service: technical agree a personalized intervention personnel to optimally configure your iPad.', 'hw'),
(7, 'Call Waiting', 'The Call Waiting service allows you to know , through a short beep , if someone is calling you while you''re busy in a conversation .\r\n\r\nAfter the warning message shown here , you may decide to temporarily suspend the current call and answer the new call , and then resume again that you have put on hold ; or you can close your conversation to take the new coming.\r\n\r\nActivation\r\n\r\nAfter requesting Notice of Call to Customer Service 187 :\r\n\r\nto activate the service : press * 43 #\r\nto deactivate the service : type # 43 #\r\nUse and query\r\n\r\nto answer the second call and return to the first : type R2\r\nto end the current call and continue with the other : type R1', 'hw'),
(8, 'Call Transfer', 'The service Transferring Call divert incoming calls from your number to a phone you''ve chosen ( fixed or mobile) when you can not answer or are busy on another call .\r\nThe person calling you will hear the message reproduced here audio_30px .\r\n\r\nActivation\r\n\r\nAfter requesting the Call Transfer to Customer Service 187 :\r\n\r\nto activate the service : press * 2 * 1 + destination telephone number + #\r\nto deactivate the service : type 1 # 2 #\r\ninterrogation\r\n\r\nto check if the service is active or not : type * 1 # 2 #', 'hw');
INSERT INTO `line_management` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `category`) VALUES
(1, 'All About Your Sim', 'All the information to manage the security PIN and PUK codes and know what to do if your SIM card lock. What are the PIN and PUK codes? \r\nThe PIN (Personal Identity Number) is a 4-digit numeric code that allows you, if you regularly set, to protect the phone from unauthorized uses. It is in fact required by phone at power; the PIN code is customizable. The PUK (Personal Unblocking Key) is a fixed and unchangeable unlock code you need to unlock the SIM as a result of the incorrect PIN code 3 times in a row. Where can I find the PIN and PUK codes? \r\nEach TIM SIM Card or subscription is sold accompanied by two security codes, PIN and PUK. You can find the PIN and PUK codes on the back of the plastic holder, which you are given when you purchase your SIM card under the silver strip. The PIN and PUK codes are strictly personal and the Customer Service 119 will provide that information in case of loss or forgetfulness.', 'line'),
(2, 'Vary The Personal Data of a TIM Rechargeable Card', 'At any time you have the ability to request the change of personal data (if you do not meet your) the number of rechargeable phone you own. \r\nYou can go to a TIM Shop with your mobile, with the SIM included and the following identification documents: \r\nFor Individuals: ID card and tax identification number; \r\nFor Legal Persons: certificate of registration with the Register of Companies (established at the Chamber of Commerce, Industry and Crafts) or, alternatively, certificate of good standing issued by the Company''s Com- mercial Section, Civil and Criminal (both issued by no later than 6 months); ID card and social security number of the owner, administrator or legal representative.', 'line'),
(3, 'Abroad With TIM', 'Using your mobile phone abroad is easy! \r\nAll TIM customers with a rechargeable line and a subscription are automatically enabled to call, receive calls, send and receive SMS from abroad.And it is as easy as in Italy! I am abroad with my rechargeable line, do I call? \r\nAll TIM customers with a rechargeable are enabled to call and receive calls abroad You have the ability to choose how to use the service according to your needs: \r\ncharging the costs directly on the remaining balance of your rechargeable; charging for the costs of the calls originated and received and sent text messages on a credit card agreement (domiciled roaming).', 'line'),
(4, 'Tim Smart', 'To you who want to surf unlimited high-speed anytime, anywhere, TIM offers the solution TIM SMART to be always connected, at home and outside the home. By TIM SMART HOUSE you: \r\nUnlimited ADSL up to 20 Mbps \r\nTIMVision included \r\nunlimited calls to fixed and mobile, with no connection fee . \r\nBy TIM SMART MOBILE you: \r\nUnlimited ADSL up to 20 Mbps \r\nTIMVision included \r\nA SIM card with 500 minutes to all Internet 2GB 4G to your Smartphone and international calls from 1 cent per minute. \r\nEverything about your home bill: a single price to satisfy needs of the whole family. \r\nAlso you can ask so many options to enrich your TIM SMART. \r\nTIM to your SMART HOUSE you can add: \r\nOPTION SMART MOBILE Smartphone: a SIM with 500 minutes to all Internet 2GB 4G to your Smartphone and international calls from 1 cent per minute. \r\nINTERNATIONAL VOICE from home: unlimited calls to landlines in the US, Canada and Western Europe. \r\nTo check if the offer is active and the availability of the services included calls for free Customer Service 187 or go to the section Fixed MyTIM . \r\nTIM to your SMART MOBILE you can add: \r\nSIM PLUS Smartphone: \r\nA SIM card with 500 minutes to all Internet 2GB 4G to your Smartphone and international calls from 1 cent per minute. \r\nSIM PLUS 4G for PC and Tablet: \r\nInternet 4G 4GB per month. \r\nNote: The SIM and SIM Plus Plus 4GB options can be activated on up to 4 mobile SIM for fixed line. \r\nVOICE MOBILE Smartphone: \r\nunlimited minutes to all. \r\nSMART HOUSE VOICE from fixed: \r\nunlimited calls to fixed and mobile, with no connection fee. \r\nINTERNATIONAL VOICE from fixed \r\nunlimited calls to the United States fixed, Canada and Western Europe \r\nTo check if the offer is active and the availability of services including call 40916 free number, Customer Service 119', 'line'),
(5, 'Activation House Line', 'A Description Request activation of a home phone line is very simple, you can: -call customer service fixed line 187\r\n-bring to you at a TIM Shop. \r\nCheck the activation mode by consulting the various deals available on line. \r\nThe necessary data are: \r\n-name and surname \r\n-tax code \r\n-home address so request the installation of the line \r\n-a mobile telephone number \r\n-email address (optional).', 'line'),
(6, 'Change Subscription', 'If you ceased your professional activities, you can request the change of your telephone subscription contract. \r\nTo request the change called the Customer Service 191. \r\nWith the request of the conversion of the contract from the Business category ("A") to the Residential category ("B") the cost of your monthly subscription will increase from: \r\n-22,50$ (excluding VAT) to 17,54$ (VAT 22 included), in case of line telephone base\r\n-31,00$ (excluding VAT) to 20,17$ (VAT 22 included), in the case of ISDN line.', 'line'),
(7, 'Turn Off Fixed Line Services', 'By registering to our Customer Area you can manage independently the cessation of active services on your tele- phone line; once you navigate de "My Line" - "Services and Offers Active" or "My Account" in the "Detail Costs" of the invoice. \r\nThe services that you can turn off are as follows:\r\n\r\n- PayForMe: is an active service by default that you can turn in "My Line" - "Summary." Click here to disable. \r\n- Who is a facility that allows you to view the display of your phone set up the number of who is calling you, from a fixed or mobile network. Clickhere to disable \r\n- Memotel: the answering machine that you can turn on your home line . \r\n- call transfer service which allows you to also transfer your mobile phone incoming calls to your home number. \r\n- Last missed call by dialing 42400 from landline you can learn the latest issue, both fixed and mobile that \r\n- called you, date and time. Alternatively: \r\n- call the Customer Service 187.', 'line');
INSERT INTO `modem_networking` (`name`, `brand`, `price`, `presentation`, `technical_characteristics`, `image`, `id`, `category`) VALUES
('3G Mobile Wi-Fi M5250', 'TP-Link', 59.9, 'Equipped with a built-in 3G modem - No additional bulky devices required\r\nHSPA+ supported with up to 21.6Mbps download and 5.76Mbps upload speeds\r\nPowerful 2000mAh battery is ideal for extended hours of outdoor use\r\nSupports up to 10 users simultaneously', 'HARDWARE FEATURES:<br>\r\nInterface: 1 micro USB port for power supply, SIM Card Slot, Micro SD card Slot<br>\r\nButton: Power On/Off Button, Reset Button<br>\r\nPower Supply: Internal 2000mAh Rechargeable Battery<br>\r\nAntenna: Internal Antenna<br>\r\nNetwork Type:<br>\r\n2G: EDGE/GPRS/GSM Quad Band \r\nMicro SD Card Reader: up to 32G<br>\r\nBand: WCDMA 2100/900MHz, GSM: 850/900/1800/1900MHz<br>\r\nLED Display: Wi-Fi status, Internet connection status, Battery Status\r\n', 'ImmaginiTIM/M25.jpg', 1, 'modem'),
('AC1200 WiFi Range Extender', 'Netgear', 49.9, 'Ultimate Range. High Power Next Generation WiFi.\r\nMaximize the power of your network and make sure you have coverage in every corner of your home with the AC1200 High Power WiFi Range Extender. Get ultimate range and performance you need for iPads, smartphones, laptops & more.', 'NETGEAR AC1200 High Power WiFi Range Extender boosts your existing network range, delivering AC dual band WiFi up to 1200Mbps. The 700mW high-power design provides ultimate range, while the dual core processor enables maximum WiFi performance. It works with any standard WiFi router and is ideal for very large homes and frustration free HD video streaming and gaming.\r\n802.11ac dual band WiFi up to 1200Mbps\r\n700mW amplified high-power design for ultimate range\r\nDual core processor for max WiFi performance', 'ImmaginiTIM/q.jpg', 2, 'modem'),
('AC1750 Smart WiFi Router', 'Netgear', 89.9, 'Maximum Speed. Optimum Ease.\r\nNext generation Gigabit WiFi technology has arrived. Get 3x faster access and more reliable streaming for your home computers and mobile devices. Beamforming+ and dual band technology makes your gaming more extreme and your HD streaming smoother.', 'Ultimate wireless coverage for large homes<br>\r\nIdeal for homes with 12 or more WiFi devices<br>\r\nNETGEAR genie App-Enjoy more of your connected home<br>\r\nWith up to 1750Mbps and a 1GHz dual core processor, you''ll be ready to support all your activities online.<br>\r\nBeamforming+ and external antennas deliver range to spare so you can stay connected throughout your home<br>\r\nDynamic QoS prioritizes network traffic by application and device<br>\r\nPowerful 1,7GHz dual-core processor boosts performance for gaming and streaming<br>\r\nTwin USB 3,0 and eSATA ports offer high-speed, USB storage-ready access', 'ImmaginiTIM/net.jpg', 3, 'modem'),
('AC750 WiFi Range Extender', 'Netgear', 39.9, 'Get ready to connect anywhere in your house with this simple-to-use WiFi Range Extender. Increase your range and reduce interference. Best of all, no dead zones to stop you from having fun on your mobile devices, smart TVs, or game consoles.', 'Improve your range with WiFi up to 750Mbps throughout your home.<br>\r\nSimultaneous dual band reduces interference and with FastLane technology, you can use both WiFi bands to establish one super high speed connection. This extender works with any standard WiFi router.<br>\r\nDual band WiFi up to 750 Mbps<br>\r\nExternal antennas for better performance\r\nConvenient wall-plug design<br>\r\nWorks with any WiFi router<br>', 'ImmaginiTIM/re.jpg', 4, 'modem'),
('G54/N150 Wireless Router', 'Netgear', 59.9, 'Simple. Secure. Superb.<br>\r\nWiFi without worry. NETGEAR makes it easy to add wireless networking in your home. Set up has never been simpler. Secure connections are as easy as the push of a button.', 'HARDWARE FEATURES:<br>\r\nInterface: 1 micro USB port for power supply, SIM Card Slot, Micro SD card Slot<br>\r\nButton: Power On/Off Button, Reset Button<br>\r\nPower Supply: Internal 2000mAh Rechargeable Battery<br>\r\nAntenna: Internal Antenna<br>\r\nNetwork Type:<br>\r\n2G: EDGE/GPRS/GSM Quad Band \r\nMicro SD Card Reader: up to 32G<br>\r\nBand: WCDMA 2100/900MHz, GSM: 850/900/1800/1900MHz<br>\r\nLED Display: Wi-Fi status, Internet connection status, Battery Status', 'ImmaginiTIM/123.jpg', 5, 'modem'),
('N300 WiFi DSL Modem Router', 'Netgear', 77.9, 'Your Modem. Your WiFi. Your Shelf Space. Why use two devices when one will do? The built-in DSL modem replaces the one from your service provider and frees up shelf space. Secure WiFi lets you share the Internet with all your computers and mobile devices for faster downloads, music and video streaming, and online gaming all at the same time. NETGEAR genie makes setup and control easy.', 'Built-in ADSL2+ Modem<br>\r\nN300 WiFi speed-Faster downloads & Internet gaming<br>\r\nReadySHARE USB-Wirelessly access & share USB storage<br>\r\nNETGEAR genie App-Home networking simplified<br>\r\nEthernet WAN-Future-proof your network', 'ImmaginiTIM/m2.jpg', 6, 'modem'),
('N300 WiFi Router', 'Netgear', 119.9, 'It''s Nice To Share. And Stream<br>\r\nA USB port lets you connect a hard drive for wireless sharing and streaming. This N300 WiFi router is ideal for medium size homes with lots of Internet activity. Live Parental Controls allow flexible filter settings, and the NETGEAR genie makes it easy to setup and monitor your network.', 'N300 WiFi speed-Faster downlaods & Internet gaming<br>\r\nReadySHARE USB- Wirelessly access & share USB storage<br>\r\nParental controls keep your Internet experience safe<br>\r\nNETGEAR genie App - Home networking simplified', 'ImmaginiTIM/m3.jpg', 7, 'modem'),
('N600 WiFi DSL Modem Router', 'Netgear', 79.9, 'Fast DSL. Dual Band WiFi. One Less Box. Now you can have fast Internet and fast WiFi all-in-one. With an integrated DSL modem you won''t need a separate modem from your service provider. N600 dual band WiFi helps keep your video streaming uninterupted. Setup and control is ultra-easy using NETGEAR genie.', 'Built-in ADSL2+ modem<br>\r\nFaster WiFi speed<br>\r\nWirelessly access & share USB hard drive & printer<br>\r\nImproves WiFi range for medium to large homes<br>\r\nNETGEAR genie App for computers, tablets, & smartphones<br>\r\nGigabit Ethernet WAN-Future-proof your network', 'ImmaginiTIM/m4.jpg', 8, 'modem'),
('Nighthawk X4S Smart WiFi Gaming Router', 'Netgear', 159.9, 'Fastest gaming performance. Unmatched processing power. Superior WiFi technology. Nighthawk X4S AC2600 Smart WiFi Router with 160MHz, MU-MIMO and Quad Stream technology delivers WiFi to multiple devices simultaneously for faster speeds. Whether gaming or streaming, you''re getting 160MHz bandwidth that ensures low-ping and best stream quality. Enjoy ultimate WiFi speeds up to 2.53Gbps, a powerful 1.7GHz dual core processor, and Dynamic QoS, delivering smoother streaming and gaming by prioritizing applications and devices. Features such as NETGEAR genie remote access, ReadyCLOUD, OpenVPN, and Kwilt app support help you manage your network, have access to a secure personal cloud, access home network remotely, and share photos stored on the storage from anywhere.', 'Quad-Stream technology delivers WiFi to multiple devices simultaneously for faster speeds<br>\r\nNext generation Wave2 WiFi-160MHz, MU-MIMO, Quad-stream<br>\r\nFour high-performance external antennas deliver maximum range<br>\r\nDynamic QoS prioritizes network traffic by application and device<br>\r\nPowerful 1,7GHz dual-core processor boosts performance for gaming and streaming<br>\r\nTwin USB 3,0 and eSATA ports offer high-speed, USB storage-ready access', 'ImmaginiTIM/m5.jpg', 9, 'modem'),
('TD-W8960N', 'TP-Link', 99.9, 'All-in-One Device: ADSL2+ Modem, NAT Router, 4-Port Switch and Wireless N Access Point<br>\r\nWireless N speed up to 300Mbps makes it ideal for heavy bandwidth consuming or interruption sensitive applications like online gaming, Internet calls and even the HD video streaming<br>\r\nEthernet WAN (EWAN) offers another broadband connectivity option for connecting to Cable, VDSL or Fiber modems<br>\r\nGuest Network Access provides secure Wi-Fi access for guests sharing your home or office network', 'HARDWARE FEATURES:<br>\r\nInterface: 1 micro USB port for power supply, SIM Card Slot, Micro SD card Slot<br>\r\nButton: Power On/Off Button, Reset Button<br>\r\nPower Supply: Internal 2000mAh Rechargeable Battery<br>\r\nAntenna: Internal Antenna<br>\r\nNetwork Type:<br>\r\n2G: EDGE/GPRS/GSM Quad Band \r\nMicro SD Card Reader: up to 32G<br>\r\nBand: WCDMA 2100/900MHz, GSM: 850/900/1800/1900MHz<br>\r\nLED Display: Wi-Fi status, Internet connection status, Battery Status', 'ImmaginiTIM/m6.jpg', 10, 'modem');
INSERT INTO `smartlife_assistance` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `category`) VALUES
(1, 'TIMGames', 'TIMgames TIM is a service dedicated to gaming that enables all customers to download on tablet and smartphone with the best games on demand and subscription to the mobile world .\r\n<br><br>\r\nWith TIMgames you will have a library of over 1,500 games, updated every week with new titles and games on offer present in the area of the store promotions.\r\n<br><br>\r\nTIMgames and accessible both from the app (downloadable from Google Play) that browsers on www.timgames.it', 'smartlife'),
(2, 'All ways to subscribe', 'With TIMgames have the opportunity to choose all the games you want for your phone in two simple ways:\r\n<br>\r\nOn demand: just log into www.timgames.it mobile version of the App or TIMgames and choose all the games present. The price is indicated for every title. In addition, within the promotions section, you will find many games to try for free before you make the purchase;<br><br>\r\nSubscription: to activate I Love Games Promo, only 2$ per week in promo for half price for the first month, you can go to any store TIM , call the 119, the 409 167 or through the website tim.it\r\nIn both cases , accessing the section MyTIMgames , you can see all the downloaded games and manage subscriptions taken.', 'smartlife'),
(3, 'Accessing TIMGames', 'You can access the TIMgames service in the following ways :\r\n<br><br>\r\nSmartphone and Tablet Android :\r\n<br>\r\nmobile version www.timgames.it\r\nTIMgames app downloadable from Google Play;<br>\r\nN.B.: With the subscription I love Games promo Active can download from TIMgames all the games you want on your Smartphone/Tablet.\r\n<br>\r\nApple and Windows Phone :\r\n<br>\r\nmobile version www.timgames.it\r\nN.B.: With the subscription I love Games promo active TIMgames can access and play all the games you want with your Smartphone / Tablet .\r\n<br><br>\r\nWith TIMgames it is very simple to play, your Smartphone / Tablet are recognized automatically and displays only compatible games.', 'smartlife'),
(4, 'Knowing the app TIMGames', 'Browse and choose the favorite games within TIMgames is simple and intuitive.\r\n<br><br>\r\nInside the home , high up there subscriptions available for your mobile. By scrolling the page down , you''ll have all the games on demand . The whole of the "free trial", you can also try out all the games you want before buying.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOnce your subscription is activated, wait for confirmation SMS. Go on timgames.it and click on the relevant signed subscription section.\r\n<br><br>\r\nTo manage your subscriptions and downloads already made, enter the reserved MyTIMgames.', 'smartlife'),
(5, 'How to see your subscription', 'To view your subscription, you can:\r\n<br><br>\r\ncome on www.timgames.it and click MyTIMgames. Inside the section "subscription management" you will find all the details of the service you signed; <br><br>\r\nenter Area Site customers tim.it and then click in the "options" <br><br>\r\nor call 40916 and seek active options on their profile.\r\n', 'smartlife'),
(6, 'How to disable a subscription', 'To deactivate your subscription , you can do:\r\n<br><br>\r\n- within the MyTIMgames clients, on the mobile site www.timgames.it<br><br>\r\n- directly online within Area customers on site tim.it<br><br>\r\n- calling freephone 40916 (Customers Rechargeable ) and following the voice guidance <br><br>\r\n- by sending a free SMS to the number 40916 with the text ILOVEGAMESPROMO OFF\r\nfree of charge by calling the Customer Service 119<br><br>', 'smartlife'),
(7, 'TIMMusic', 'TIMmusic is the digital music platform Telecomitalia dedicated to all customers who have a smartphone/tablet TIM or an ADSL line or residential Fiber Telecom Italy or internet stick TIM.\r\n<br><br>\r\nWith TIMmusic can listen to millions of songs streaming with no time limit on your smartphone and tablet or PC (ADSL and Fiber customers Residential Telecom Italy or internet stick TIM). You can create your own playlists or listen to those suggested by famous DJs and artists and share all your favorite social network. The catalog is constantly updated with all the latest releases, often in exclusive preview . And, if you are mobile, not because consumption GB data traffic for listening to music is included in the subscription fee.', 'smartlife'),
(8, 'All ways to buy', 'If you are a TIM customer can activate the subscription for Smarthone and tablet directly in the Subscription of App. For iOS you will need access from your smartphone or tablet to timmusic.it\r\n<br><br>\r\nYou can turn also TIMmusic at TIM stores, by calling 40916 (following the voice guide) or tim.it (for TIM stick).\r\n<br><br>\r\nIf you are a residential customer with an ADSL or Fibre Telecom Italian line you can activate the subscription in order to enjoy TIMmusic PC, from site timmusic.it, from tim.it website or by calling 187.', 'smartlife');
