('Huawei MediaPad T2 10.0 Pro LTE', 'Huawei', 359.9, 'Huawei MediaPad T2 10.0 Pro LTE tablet was launched in April 2016. The tablet comes with a 10.10-inch display with a resolution of 1200 pixels by 1920 pixels at a PPI of 224 pixels per inch. \r\nThe Huawei MediaPad T2 10.0 Pro LTE is powered by 1.2GHz octa-core Qualcomm Snapdragon 616 processor and it comes with 2GB of RAM. The tablet packs 16GB of internal storage cannot be expanded. As far as the cameras are concerned, the Huawei MediaPad T2 10.0 Pro LTE packs a 8-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 2-megapixel front shooter for selfies. \r\nThe Huawei MediaPad T2 10.0 Pro LTE runs Android 5.1 and is powered by a 6660mAh non removable battery. It measures 259.10 x 156.40 x 8.50 (height x width x thickness) and weighs 495.00 grams. ', 'GENERAL\r\nRelease date	April 2016\r\nDimensions (mm)	259.10 x 156.40 x 8.50\r\nWeight (g)	495.00\r\nBattery capacity (mAh)	6660\r\nRemovable battery	No\r\nColours	Pearl White, Charcoal Black\r\nSAR value	0.00\r\nDISPLAY\r\nScreen size (inches)	10.10\r\nResolution	1200x1920 pixels\r\nPixels per inch (PPI)	224\r\nHARDWARE\r\nProcessor	1.2GHz  octa-core\r\nProcessor make	Qualcomm Snapdragon 616\r\nRAM	2GB\r\nInternal storage	16GB\r\nCAMERA\r\nRear camera	8-megapixel\r\nFlash	Yes\r\nFront camera	2-megapixel\r\nSOFTWARE\r\nOperating System	Android 5.1\r\nSkin	Emotion UI 3.1\r\nCONNECTIVITY\r\nWi-Fi	Yes\r\nWi-Fi standards supported	NA\r\nGPS	Yes\r\nBluetooth	Yes\r\nNFC	No\r\nInfrared	No\r\nUSB OTG	Yes\r\nHeadphones	3.5mm\r\nFM	Yes\r\nSIM Type	Micro-SIM\r\nGSM/ CDMA	GSM\r\n3G	Yes\r\n4G/ LTE	Yes\r\nSupports 4G in India (Band 40)	Yes\r\nVoice Calling	No\r\nSENSORS\r\nCompass/ Magnetometer	No\r\nProximity sensor	Yes\r\nAccelerometer	Yes\r\nAmbient light sensor	Yes\r\nGyroscope	Yes\r\nBarometer	No\r\nTemperature sensor	No', 'ImmaginiTIM/tab2.jpg', 3, 'tablet'),
